{"tid":602046,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拉脫維亞展覽網上直播「食自己」　即場割肉煎熟放入口","createTime":"2018-03-22T17:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T05:39:30.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f037b52d42c8b951e03fe60b047b205939340211","tid":602046,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拉脫維亞展覽網上直播「食自己」　即場割肉煎熟放入口</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180322/s00005/fbb5ca7f0bbdf6a415fc31c59f3e448d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180322%2Fs00005%2Ffbb5ca7f0bbdf6a415fc31c59f3e448d.jpg&h=6602752c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉脫維亞藝術家Arturs Bērziņ&scaron;，為表達人類在末日後，因食物不足會同類相食，在網上直播「食人」，請來兩位助手即場吞食自己背部「新鮮」肉塊。展覽3月6日在該國首都里加一間博物館舉行。警方正調查事件，希望搜集資料提出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n影片開始，一男一女站在表演台上，背後有投影機投射閃電和怒海片段，並播着雜音和悲壯樂聲。二人其後坐在台中白椅上，有位穿上白色防護衣人士，用手術刀割下他們背部一小撮肉，致使鮮血直流。雖然事前未見二人注射麻醉藥，但他們割肉前後仍然坐得筆直，身體未有抽搐。<br />\n<br />\n施刀者用叉挑起「人肉」，放入加熱中的平底鍋上，加入調味料，又翻起肉塊，確保兩邊都有煎過，其後用叉將煎熟「人肉」餵給兩人，其中男的嘴唇動了一下。貝多芬第9號交響曲第四樂章、歐盟盟歌基礎《歡樂頌》隨着雜音奏起，兩位人士面向舞台，觀眾拍手，影片緩緩變得昏暗，閉幕。<br />\n<br />\n片段在網上惹來不少反彈。警方目前正調查事件，暫未能肯定肉塊是否真的從人體切下來。<br />\n<br />\n(每日郵報/太陽報)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4GMDS9xL3d4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4GMDS9xL3d4&d=BIfqzdE3o7%2BAwe8XhhNjbE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=3b9b8f68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4GMDS9xL3d4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180322/s00005/1521693135040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180322%2Fs00005%2F1521693135040&d=BIfqzdE3o7%2BAwe8XhhNjbE4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=e00ee1fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180322%2Fs00005%2F1521693135040&h=ad38e1a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180322/s00005/1521693135040</a>"},{"pid":"ae2a40a274e70f80f0d76bad6e5b2e59e1bb7875","tid":602046,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3845a2bca3971ddf9236b3a50d8b691ce09d0418","tid":602046,"uid":14606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"我會想嘔係咪我晤正常"},{"pid":"a5fc09269fad571370099fc3ed67466394e1d734","tid":602046,"uid":74751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d40941d0bbbbccb17b07684cc31c0782dc9050","tid":602046,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46676d363ab9fe7d3d27aade26d80c9e8e65f55","tid":602046,"uid":3457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3845a2bca3971ddf9236b3a50d8b691ce09d0418","tid":602046,"uid":14606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"我會想嘔係咪我晤正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"素食撚全面進場"},{"pid":"6d52dd7c0339ec8bc17c47f6bd871f9ff0f65a41","tid":602046,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"屌那媽睇到好想嘔"},{"pid":"f8f44dcfd82d50fb795542cf336676039f667cd0","tid":602046,"uid":41311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"藝術=垃圾"},{"pid":"589267a1e9e078add5c727c055ea2879ad4b94f5","tid":602046,"uid":106027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"之前日本有單 畀人拉咗"},{"pid":"ac4a4074a3ad2dce4e5cf9d8626